OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,FCommenting on the strike action, EIS-
OL,7,FFELA President Anne-Marie Harley said:
OL,8,F"Once again EIS-FELA members are being
OL,9,Fforced to take strike action in
OL,10,Fpursuit of a fair pay offer.
OL,12,F"It is a disgrace that in 2024 our
OL,13,Fmembers are living on 2021 wages,
OL,14,Famidst the worst cost of living crisis
OL,15,Fin generations.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
