OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,FMs Harley added: "Members have been
OL,7,Finformed that there will be cuts to
OL,8,Fservices and courses for students,
OL,9,Fcreating barriers and fewer learning
OL,10,Fopportunities for those students
OL,11,Faccessing college education.
OL,13,F"College principals have further added
OL,14,Ffuel to the fire by threatening to
OL,15,Fwithhold pay from our lecturers who
OL,16,Fare taking part in action short of
OL,17,Fstrike action.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
