OL,6,FIn response a Scottish Government
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "While the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment respects the right of trade
OL,9,Funions to take industrial action, we
OL,10,Fremain concerned about the potential
OL,11,Fimpacts this action will have on
OL,12,Fstudents. We expect colleges to put in
OL,13,Fplace mitigations to minimise
OL,14,Fdisruption.
OL,26,@oD@TOU
