OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,F"It is of course for the college
OL,7,Funions and employers to negotiate pay,
OL,8,Fterms and conditions, not the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment. However, Ministers are
OL,10,Fencouraging both sides to come to a
OL,11,Fresolution and bring this action to a
OL,12,Fclose.
OL,14,F"The Further Education Minister will
OL,15,Fcontinue to engage with both
OL,16,Fmanagement and unions as they work to
OL,17,Freach a settlement that is fair and
OL,18,Faffordable."
