OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,FGavin Donoghue, CES (College Employers
OL,7,FScotland) Director, said: "Further
OL,8,Fstrikes by the EIS-FELA will not, and
OL,9,Fcannot, lead to an improved pay offer
OL,10,Ffrom college employers, only more
OL,11,Fdisruption for students.
OL,13,F"The #5,000 full and final pay offer
OL,14,Fis already at the limits of
OL,15,Faffordability for colleges, and is set
OL,16,Fagainst years of real-terms budget
OL,17,Fcuts and now a cash cut of over #32
OL,18,Fmillion.
