OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,F"Despite unprecedented financial
OL,7,Fpressures, colleges have put forward a
OL,8,Fsubstantial pay offer for lecturers
OL,9,Fwhich, if accepted by the EIS-FELA,
OL,10,Fwould keep college lecturers in
OL,11,FScotland as the best paid in the whole
OL,12,FUK.
OL,14,F"The EIS-FELA should put this offer to
OL,15,Fits members in a formal ballot, as it
OL,16,Fwould deliver an 11.5% average pay
OL,17,Fincrease for college lecturers from
OL,18,FSeptember, and give those at the start
OL,19,Fof the National Pay Scale a rise of
OL,20,F14.2%.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
