OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,F"The pay offer would also mean that
OL,7,Fthe average college lecturer is almost
OL,8,F#1,500 better off than they would be
OL,9,Funder Public Sector Pay Policy.
OL,11,F"Employers have also acknowledged the
OL,12,FEIS-FELA's concern about job security
OL,13,Fand have agreed in writing to the
OL,14,Ftrade union's suggested wording that
OL,15,Fany compulsory redundancies would not
OL,16,Fbe directly related to the full and
OL,17,Ffinal pay offer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
