OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,F"Colleges simply cannot offer to give
OL,7,Fwhat they do not have, especially when
OL,8,Fgovernment funding is set to fall by
OL,9,Fnearly 5% in 2024/25. The Scottish
OL,10,FGovernment has confirmed on a number
OL,11,Fof occasions that it will not fund a
OL,12,Fpay award in the college sector.
OL,14,F"We urge the EIS-FELA to cancel its
OL,15,Findustrial action and put the
OL,16,Femployers' full and final pay offer to
OL,17,Fits members in a formal ballot."
